            <title><![CDATA[Video: 13 Exciting New Games Coming To Switch 1 & 2 In March 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://www.nintendolife.com/news/2026/03/video-13-exciting-new-games-coming-to-switch-1-and-2-in-march-2026</link>
